OL,3,CMum's warning after daughter's
OL,4,Cketamine death
OL,6,FThe mother of a young woman who died
OL,7,Ffollowing a ketamine addiction has
OL,8,Fwarned others that the drug "destroys
OL,9,Feverything around you".
OL,11,FTracy Marelli said her daughter,
OL,12,FSophie Russell, went from being "a
OL,13,Fpretty young girl" when she first took
OL,14,Fthe party drug aged 18 to resembling
OL,15,F"an elderly lady" by the time she died
OL,16,Fat the age of 20.
OL,18,FTracy, from Lincoln, is now calling
OL,19,Ffor Ketamine to be reclassified from a
OL,20,Fclass B to a class A drug.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
