OL,3,CMum's warning after daughter's
OL,4,Cketamine death
OL,6,F"It took her head - that drug
OL,7,Fdestroyed her head," she said. "She
OL,8,Flooked like an elderly lady towards
OL,9,Fthe end.
OL,11,F"It's a huge risk to take, to even go
OL,12,Fnear it. She always said to me she
OL,13,Fcouldn't get away from it. It's not
OL,14,Fworth destroying your family and
OL,15,Fyourself over it. It destroys
OL,16,Feverything around you."
