OL,3,CMum's warning after daughter's
OL,4,Cketamine death
OL,6,FSophie, who Tracy described as a
OL,7,F"massive ball of energy", first
OL,8,Fexperimented with ketamine on a night
OL,9,Fout after losing her grandmother in
OL,10,F2021.
OL,12,FShe quickly became addicted, but hid
OL,13,Fher habit from her mother until she
OL,14,Fstarted showing signs of drug use like
OL,15,Fbruising on her arms and legs, slurred
OL,16,Fspeech and recurring stomach pains.
OL,18,FWhat is ketamine?
OL,20,FKetamine is an injectable anaesthetic
OL,21,Fthat has hallucinogenic effects.
