OL,6,FIt distorts perceptions of sight and
OL,7,Fsound and makes the user feel
OL,8,Fdisconnected and not in control.
OL,10,FAlong with the other "club drugs" it
OL,11,Fhas become popular among teens and
OL,12,Fyoung adults and is manufactured
OL,13,Fcommercially as a powder or liquid and
OL,14,Fcan be snorted or swallowed.
OL,16,FShort-term effects can include memory
OL,17,Floss, impaired judgement,
OL,18,Fdisorientation, clumsiness and anxiety
