OL,6,FRegular users may experience
OL,7,Fflashbacks, mood and personality
OL,8,Fchanges, depression, concentration
OL,9,Fproblems and abdominal pain.
OL,11,FAn overdose can cause unconsciousness
OL,12,Fand dangerously slowed breathing.
OL,14,FIn January 2023 Tracy found evidence
OL,15,Fof drug taking in her daughter's room.
OL,17,FShe said Sophie sought help but
OL,18,Fquickly deteriorated.
OL,20,F"The weight loss was incredible," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
