OL,3,CMum's warning after daughter's
OL,4,Cketamine death
OL,6,F"She was a (dress) size 14 to 16 at
OL,7,Fthe age of 18, to just over six stone
OL,8,Fwhen she passed away. Numerous times
OL,9,Fwe went to the doctors about weight
OL,10,Floss, pains in her stomach.
OL,12,F"From a sociable girl she became
OL,13,Fsomeone who just stayed in her room.
OL,15,F"I became her carer, but I did think
OL,16,Fshe would get through it."
OL,18,FSophie managed to break from drug use
OL,19,Ffor brief periods during holidays and
OL,20,Fdetoxification treatment.
