OL,6,FBut in September last year she became
OL,7,Fseriously ill when she visited her
OL,8,Ffather's home to stay overnight. She
OL,9,Fwas discovered the next day.
OL,11,FTracy said: "I fell to the ground and
OL,12,Fscreamed and I can still hear the
OL,13,Fscream in my head now."
OL,15,FThe coroner at her inquest on Thursday
OL,16,Fconcluded Sophie died from a cardiac
OL,17,Farrest caused by chronic use.
OL,19,FTracy said young people were unaware
OL,20,Fof the potential dangers of the drug.
